articles.title: Naomi Osaka makes grand entrance and big fashion statement at Australian Open - AP News
articles.description: Naomi Osaka has made a fashion statement and quite an entrance to the Australian Open. Osaka was wearing a wide-brim hat, veil and holding a white parasol as she walked onto Rod Laver Arena for her first-round match. The No. 16 seed then won a tough three-set…
